### PTMode
PTModes are the modes of transport.
At the PTMode level, there are the following values (there are more, but we don’t use them, even of the ones mentioned below, not all are currently used):
- unknown
- rail
- coach
- suburbanRail
- urbanRail
- metro
- underground
- bus
- trolleybus
- tram
- water
- air
- telecabin
- funicular
- taxi
- selfDrive
- all
The SubModes are:
AirSubmode
- Currently not used
BusSubmode
- regionalBus
- expressBus
- localBus
- postBus
- sightseeing-bus
- shuttleBus
- railReplacementBus
- demandAndResponseBus
CoachSubmode
- internationalCoachService
- nationalCoachService
- regionalCoachService
- touristCoachService
FunicularSubmode
- funicular
MetroSubmode
- urbanRailway
- metro
Tram submode
- cityTram
